title: #95: Apodcalypse Bug Out Bag with Jonathan Kite and Gabby Bryan
description: Thank you for tuning in for another fun episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli.  Today Sam and Ryan welcome comedian actor Jonathan Kite and from the Apodcalypse podcast Gabby Bryan to talk what you should have in your apocalypse survival bag.  Thank you so much for all of your support.
